Package: mappeR
Type: Package
Title: Construct and Visualize TDA Mapper Graphs
Description: An implementation of various flavors of the mapper 
  algorithm (from the field of topological data analysis) in R, which is able 
  to pass data to Cytoscape for detailed visualization and further analysis.
